{"tid":1180733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"地鐵痴漢非禮女學生後逃跑 日本大叔伸出正義一腳KO","createTime":"2019-06-01T05:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T03:21:23.000Z","uid":38631,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cf89a41b5d02a82adbfeefc211bb3b50625d29f3","tid":1180733,"uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:18:09.000Z","msg":"日前，東京JR赤羽站發生懷疑痴漢非禮女學生事件，女學生在月台向涉事痴漢大叫「不要跑」並飛奔追捕時，一位在月台等車的大叔仗義伸出一腳把痴漢絆倒，最後在職員協助下成功把涉事痴漢制服。<br />\n<br />\n5月28日，東京JR赤羽站月台女學生飛奔追捕一名中年男人，幸得一名仗義大叔伸腳絆倒該名痴漢，最後成功將他制服。據悉，當時女學生被該名痴漢非禮胸部，而且騷擾行為並不止一次，持續近一個月。女學生最後忍無可忍，在月台追捕痴漢，幸得大叔仗義伸腳幫忙絆倒痴漢。涉事痴漢其後承認非禮被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/01/3yz4xO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F01%2F3yz4xO.png&h=4958fa9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/01/f5NU4H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F01%2Ff5NU4H.png&h=fc612a53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/01/YWhloP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F01%2FYWhloP.png&h=bd97f98d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/06/01/gpRUzy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F06%2F01%2FgpRUzy.png&h=72ecee4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n影片在網上掀起熱議，有網民大讚女學生行為勇敢，亦讚月台大叔行為正義。<br />\n<br />\n完整影片：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZEnIV_P6I_w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZEnIV_P6I_w&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=5d871a42\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZEnIV_P6I_w</a>"},{"pid":"15d26cdcfc76bee53265fc302e9f321e1c507e73","tid":1180733,"uid":38631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:19:41.000Z","msg":"配樂配得幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3383829a17126dac1632b692d382f1834ee73cb","tid":1180733,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:30:50.000Z","msg":"個大叔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54b5d589e7d9a25eac686ff6ab168f9c7d02af6","tid":1180733,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e1b95afb1dfcc610e0746d4cc92763327227158","tid":1180733,"uid":253574,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"佢可能真係痴漢嚟嘅<br />\n但聽講日本比人屈非禮<br />\n都好高機率入罪吓<br />\n其實係咪點都要跑走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"701abdb53f8965d06560c0bd069e11f21c7f6226","tid":1180733,"uid":163111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:49:37.000Z","msg":"阿叔肯定踢開後衛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f321820ed07932c60f07d25e8c8eaa4a51126a79","tid":1180733,"uid":53065,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0e1b95afb1dfcc610e0746d4cc92763327227158","tid":1180733,"uid":253574,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"佢可能真係痴漢嚟嘅<br />\n但聽講日本比人屈非禮<br />\n都好高機率入罪吓<br />\n其實係咪點都要跑走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:49:56.000Z","msg":"yes！捉到100%"},{"pid":"718fd4490929fb51739eb7bc297354b2d48a4e4d","tid":1180733,"uid":92479,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0e1b95afb1dfcc610e0746d4cc92763327227158","tid":1180733,"uid":253574,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"佢可能真係痴漢嚟嘅<br />\n但聽講日本比人屈非禮<br />\n都好高機率入罪吓<br />\n其實係咪點都要跑走？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:55:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://8maple.ru/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/242721.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg